[32m+[m[32m# PART 2: DATA RECOVERY (DC) PLAN[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## 2.1 What Data Needs Protection?[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m| Data Type | File/Location | Backup Frequency | Recovery Method |[m
[32m+[m[32m|-----------|---------------|-----------------|------------------|[m
[32m+[m[32m| Complaints Database | data/complaintiq.sqlite | Hourly | Restore from backup |[m
[32m+[m[32m| ML Models | models/*.joblib | On retrain | Re-run training scripts |[m
