[32m+[m[32m2. Store in backup directory: data/backups/[m
[32m+[m[32m3. Keep last 24 hourly backups[m
[32m+[m[32m4. Clean up older backups (keep daily, weekly)[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Tier 2: Daily Full Backups[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mPROCEDURE:[m
[32m+[m[32m1. Backup SQLite database[m
[32m+[m[32m2. Backup ML model files (.joblib)[m
[32m+[m[32m3. Backup ChromaDB (vector store)[m
