[32m+[m[32m4. Monthly review for important archives[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## 2.3 Recovery Procedures[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Quick Restore (< 30 minutes)[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32m1. Stop application[m
