[32m+[m[32m# PART 3: BUSINESS CONTINUITY PLANNING (BCP)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## 3.1 What is Business Continuity?[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mBusiness Continuity means the system KEEPS WORKING even when something fails. It's not about recovery - it's about resilience.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## 3.2 Our Current Fallback Architecture (Already Implemented!)[m
[32m+[m
