[32m+[m[32m- Returns rule-based defaults if model fails[m
[32m+[m[32m- Logs error for monitoring[m
[32m+[m[32mRESULT: Predictions still work (just less accurate)[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Fallback 3: ChromaDB Unavailable[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
