[32m+[m[32mRESULT: Minor feature loss, core functions work[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Fallback 4: Database Unavailable[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mWHAT HAPPENS: SQLite file locked or corrupted[m
[32m+[m[32mOUR PROTECTION:[m
[32m+[m[32m- Error handling around all DB operations[m
