[32m+[m[32m## How It Works (Mathematical Explanation)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Step 1: Feature Engineering**[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m30+ features created from each complaint:[m
[32m+[m[32m- `pct_sla_elapsed` = hours_since_filed / (days_to_sla × 24)[m
[32m+[m[32m- `is_duplicate` = Is this a duplicate complaint?[m
[32m+[m[32m- `severity_score` = Critical=4, High=3, Medium=2, Low=1[m
[32m+[m[32m- `sentiment_score` = Angry=4, Frustrated=3, Neutral=2, Polite=1[m
[32m+[m[32m- `category_*` = One-hot encoded categories[m
[32m+[m[32m- `channel_risk` = Twitter/WhatsApp = 1 (public channels)[m
[32m+[m[32m- `is_fraud_keyword` = Contains "fraud", "unauthorized" = 1[m
[32m+[m[32m- `is_repeat_customer` = Has filed more than 1 complaint[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Step 2: Decision Trees**[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mEach tree makes splits:[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mif pct_sla_elapsed > 0.8:[m
[32m+[m[32m    if severity_score >= 3:[m
[32m+[m[32m        BREACH[m
[32m+[m[32m    else:[m
[32m+[m[32m        CHECK_OTHER[m
[32m+[m[32melse:[m
[32m+[m[32m    if is_duplicate == 0:[m
[32m+[m[32m        LIKELY_NO_BREACH[m
[32m+[m[32m    else:[m
[32m+[m[32m        CHECK_OTHER[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Step 3: Gradient Boosting**[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mTree 1: Predicts 0.4 (40% chance of breach)[m
[32m+[m[32mTree 2: Sees Tree 1's error = actual 0.6, predicts +0.15 correction[m
[32m+[m[32mTree 3: Sees Tree 2's error, predicts +0.10 correction[m
[32m+[m[32m...[m
[32m+[m[32mTree 200: Final = 0.4 + 0.15 + 0.10 + ... = 0.78 (78% chance)[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Step 4: Regularization (What makes XGBoost special)**[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mXGBoost penalizes complex trees to prevent overfitting:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mObjective = Loss + λ × Σ(w²) + γ × T[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- w = leaf weights (smaller = simpler)[m
[32m+[m[32m- T = number of leaves (fewer = simpler)[m
[32m+[m[32m- λ = L2 regularization[m
[32m+[m[32m- γ = L1 regularization[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
