[32m+[m[32m# Model 2: Category Classifier (TF-IDF + Logistic Regression)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## What It Does[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mClassifies complaint text into one of 6 categories: **UPI, ATM, Card, Loan, NetBanking, General**[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Why We Need It[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mDifferent categories have different:[m
[32m+[m[32m- SLA windows (UPI=5 days, Loan=30 days)[m
[32m+[m[32m- Teams handling them[m
[32m+[m[32m- Resolution procedures[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## How It Works (Simple Explanation)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Step 1: TF-IDF - Convert Text to Numbers**[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mTF-IDF assigns importance scores to words:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32m"UPI payment failed" →[m[41m [m
[32m+[m[32m- "UPI" = HIGH weight (rare but specific)[m
[32m+[m[32m- "payment" = MEDIUM weight[m
[32m+[m[32m- "failed" = HIGH weight[m
[32m+[m[32m- "the" = ZERO weight (too common)[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mFormula:[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mTF-IDF(word) = (1 + log(TF)) × log(N / DF)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mTF = term frequency in document[m
[32m+[m[32mDF = documents containing term[m
[32m+[m[32mN = total documents[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Step 2: Logistic Regression - Classify**[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThink of it as a weighted voting system:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mWord Weights for "UPI" category:[m
[32m+[m[32m- "UPI" = +5.2[m
[32m+[m[32m- "payment" = +1.3[m
[32m+[m[32m- "failed" = +0.8[m
[32m+[m[32m- "card" = -3.1 (signals "Card", not "UPI")[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mComplaint: "UPI payment failed"[m
[32m+[m[32mScore = 5.2 + 1.3 + 0.8 = 7.3 → HIGH UPI probability[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mUses **softmax** to convert scores to probabilities:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mP(UPI) = exp(score_UPI) / (exp(score_UPI) + exp(score_ATM) + ... + exp(score_General))[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Feature Engineering[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- TF-IDF with (1,2) n-grams (captures "credit card" as one phrase)[m
[32m+[m[32m- Max 10,000 features[m
[32m+[m[32m- Sublinear TF scaling (1 + log(TF))[m
[32m+[m[32m- Unicode accent stripping (for Hindi/Marathi)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Visual: TF-IDF Weight Calculation[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32m┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐[m
[32m+[m[32m│                      TF-IDF WEIGHT CALCULATION                                  │[m
[32m+[m[32m├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤[m
[32m+[m[32m│                                                                                 │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  Complaint: "UPI payment of Rs.5000 failed, money debited"                     │[m
[32m+[m[32m│                                                                                 │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  STEP 1: Count Term Frequency (TF)                                      │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────                 │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "UPI"       → appears 1 time    → TF = 1                             │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "payment"   → appears 1 time    → TF = 1                             │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "failed"    → appears 1 time    → TF = 1                             │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "money"     → appears 1 time    → TF = 1                             │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "the"       → appears 1 time    → TF = 1                             │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│                                    │                                           │[m
[32m+[m[32m│                                    ▼                                           │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  STEP 2: Calculate IDF (Inverse Document Frequency)                   │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────                 │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  IDF = log(N / DF)  where N = total docs, DF = docs containing term    │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │                                                                          │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "UPI"     → appears in 50 of 1000 docs → IDF = log(1000/50) = 3.0   │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "failed"  → appears in 200 of 1000 docs → IDF = log(1000/200) = 1.6 │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "the"     → appears in 1000 of 1000 docs → IDF = log(1) = 0.0       │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "money"   → appears in 300 of 1000 docs → IDF = log(1000/300) = 1.2  │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│                                    │                                           │[m
[32m+[m[32m│                                    ▼                                           │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  STEP 3: TF × IDF = Final Weight                                       │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────                 │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │                                                                          │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "UPI"     → 1 × 3.0 = 3.0  ← HIGH (rare but important!)              │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "failed"  → 1 × 1.6 = 1.6  ← MEDIUM                                   │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "money"   → 1 × 1.2 = 1.2  ← MEDIUM                                   │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │  "the"     → 1 × 0.0 = 0.0  ← ZERO (too common!)                      │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  │                                                                          │    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │[m
[32m+[m[32m│                                                                                 │[m
[32m+[m[32m└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Results[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Accuracy:** 97%[m
[32m+[m[32m- **LLM Agreement:** 98%[m
