[32m+[m[32m## Two Components Explained[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Component 1: Sentence-Transformers[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mModel: `all-MiniLM-L6-v2`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Creates 384-dimensional embeddings for any text[m
[32m+[m[32m- Trained on millions of sentence pairs[m
[32m+[m[32m- Captures SEMANTIC meaning, not just keywords[m
[32m+[m[32m- CPU inference in <50ms[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mInput: "UPI payment failed, money debited"[m
[32m+[m[32mOutput: [0.12, -0.45, 0.67, -0.23, 0.89, ...] (384 numbers)[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Component 2: ChromaDB[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mChromaDB is a vector database:[m
[32m+[m[32m- Stores embeddings + metadata[m
[32m+[m[32m- Efficient similarity search[m
[32m+[m[32m- Persistent storage (saves to disk)[m
[32m+[m[32m- Cosine similarity space[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```python[m
[32m+[m[32m# Store embeddings[m
[32m+[m[32mcollection.upsert([m
[32m+[m[32m    ids=["UBI-0001"],[m
[32m+[m[32m    embeddings=[embedding_vector],[m
[32m+[m[32m    documents=["complaint text"],[m
[32m+[m[32m    metadatas=[{"customer_name": "John", "category": "UPI"}][m
[32m+[m[32m)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m# Query for duplicates[m
[32m+[m[32mresults = collection.query([m
[32m+[m[32m    query_embeddings=[new_embedding],[m
[32m+[m[32m    n_results=5,[m
[32m+[m[32m    where={"customer_name": "John"}  # Only same customer![m
[32m+[m[32m)[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## The Algorithm[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m1. **Index:** Embed ALL existing complaints, store in ChromaDB[m
[32m+[m[32m2. **Query:** For new complaint, embed its text[m
[32m+[m[32m3. **Search:** Find top-5 similar complaints FROM SAME CUSTOMER[m
[32m+[m[32m4. **Compare:** If similarity ≥ 0.78 → DUPLICATE[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Why Same Customer Only?[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mDifferent customers complaining about "UPI failed"[m
[32m+[m[32m→ NOT a duplicate[m
[32m+[m[32m→ This is a SYSTEMIC ISSUE (handled by Root Cause Agent)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mSame customer complaining about "UPI failed" again[m
[32m+[m[32m→ IS a duplicate[m
[32m+[m[32m→ Auto-resolve without drafting new response[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Key Parameters[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Embedding Model:** all-MiniLM-L6-v2 (384 dimensions)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Similarity Threshold:** 0.78 (cosine similarity)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Top-K:** 5 nearest neighbors searched[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Search Scope:** Same customer only (not all complaints)[m
[32m+[m
