[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## 3.7 Model 7: Customer Risk Score (Weighted Formula) (2 minutes)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m> "Seventh and final - calculating customer risk.[m
[32m+[m[32m>[m
[32m+[m[32m> **The Problem It Solves:**[m
[32m+[m[32m> Not all customers are equal risk. Some will escalate to RBI Ombudsman. Some might leave the bank (churn). Some might cause social media backlash. We need to identify HIGH-RISK customers for proactive management.[m
[32m+[m[32m>[m
[32m+[m[32m> **Our Solution: Three Sub-Scores + Weighted Composite**[m
[32m+[m[32m>[m
[32m+[m[32m> **1. RBI Ombudsman Escalation Risk (45% weight)**[m
[32m+[m[32m> Based on:[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Breach probability from our SLA model (×40)[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Severity (Critical=30, High=20, Medium=10, Low=3)[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Repeat complaints (up to +15)[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Amount involved (≥1L = +12, ≥25k = +6)[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Angry sentiment history (up to +8)[m
[32m+[m[32m>[m
[32m+[m[32m> **2. Churn Risk (30% weight)**[m
[32m+[m[32m> Based on:[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Total complaints × 6[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Unresolved count × 5[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Category breadth × 6 (touched many categories = systemic dissatisfaction)[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Current sentiment/severity[m
[32m+[m[32m>[m
[32m+[m[32m> **3. Social Media Risk (25% weight)**[m
[32m+[m[32m> Based on:[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Twitter/WhatsApp complaints × 12 (public visibility)[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Current channel = Twitter/WhatsApp (+18)[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Angry sentiment (+22) or Frustrated (+10)[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Critical severity (+8)[m
[32m+[m[32m>[m
[32m+[m[32m> **Composite Formula:**[m
[32m+[m[32m> ```[m
[32m+[m[32m> Overall Risk = 0.45 × ombudsman + 0.30 × churn + 0.25 × social[m
[32m+[m[32m> ```[m
[32m+[m[32m>[m
[32m+[m[32m> **Why These Weights?**[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Ombudsman (45%): Highest business impact - RBI fines + reputation[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Churn (30%): Customer retention is crucial[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Social (25%): Public visibility matters but less than formal escalation[m
[32m+[m[32m>[m
[32m+[m[32m> **Results:**[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Low risk (0-30): ~60% of customers[m
[32m+[m[32m> - Medium risk (31-60): ~30%[m
[32m+[m[32m> - High risk (61-100): ~10%[m
[32m+[m[32m>[m
[32m+[m[32m> This helps identify customers who need proactive attention BEFORE they escalate.[m
[32m+[m[32m>[m
