[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Q22: How do the ML models integrate with the LLM pipeline?[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**A:** "Two-stage architecture:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Stage 1 (LLM Processing):**[m
[32m+[m[32m1. Intake Agent → Extracts structured fields using Groq LLaMA[m
[32m+[m[32m2. Classifier Agent → Assigns category/severity/sentiment using LLM[m
[32m+[m[32m3. Duplicate Detector → Finds similar complaints[m
[32m+[m[32m4. Response Drafter → Creates reply in customer's language[m
[32m+[m[32m5. Root Cause → Clusters for systemic issues[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Stage 2 (ML Verification):**[m
[32m+[m[32mAfter the LLM classifies, we run our ML models as second opinions:[m
[32m+[m[32m- ML Category (TF-IDF) → Verifies LLM category[m
[32m+[m[32m- ML Sentiment (RoBERTa) → Verifies LLM sentiment[m
[32m+[m[32m- SLA Monitor (XGBoost) → Predicts breach probability[m
[32m+[m[32m- Priority Scorer (GBM) → Scores urgency[m
[32m+[m[32m- Risk Score → Calculates customer risk[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mBoth LLM and ML results are stored in the database and displayed on the dashboard. The key point: ML models are SECOND opinions, not replacements. LLM remains primary, ML provides verification."[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Q23: What happens if the LLM API is unavailable?[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**A:** "Every agent has a deterministic fallback:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Intake**: Returns minimal fields extracted from text[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Classifier**: Uses regex patterns for category, severity heuristics[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Response Drafter**: Returns 'Please contact support' template[m
[32m+[m[32m- **SLA Monitor**: Uses rule-based probability calculation[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe pipeline NEVER fails - always returns a result. If the LLM is down, we fall back to heuristic-based processing.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThis ensures the system is resilient to API failures."[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
