[32m+[m[32m## 2.1 The Scale of the Problem[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mLet me paint a picture with numbers:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Union Bank of India** alone has millions of customers[m
[32m+[m[32m- Each month, hundreds of thousands of complaints flow in across **7 distinct channels**: email, WhatsApp, Twitter, phone calls, branch visits, net banking portal, and mobile app[m
