[32m+[m[32m{[m
[32m+[m[32m    "bucket": "negative",[m
[32m+[m[32m    "score": 0.87[m
[32m+[m[32m}[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Step 5: Agent 3 - Duplicate Detector (ChromaDB)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Input**: Complaint text + customer_name[m
[32m+[m[32m**Process**:[m
[32m+[m[32m1. Embed text: `[0.12, -0.34, 0.56, ...]` (384-dim)[m
