[32m+[m[32m- RBI mandates strict **SLA (Service Level Agreement)** deadlines[m
[32m+[m[32m- Failure to meet SLA results in **penalties** and **customer escalation** to RBI Ombudsman[m
[32m+[m[32m- Customers expect responses in their **own language** (English, Hindi, Marathi)[m
