[32m+[m[32m## 2. Why Traditional Solutions Fail[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### A) Rule-Based Systems Don't Work[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mTraditional approach: Write rules like "IF text contains 'UPI' THEN category = UPI"[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Why it fails:**[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mComplaint: "My phone pay is not working, I tried to transfer 5000 rupees"[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mRule-based:[m[41m [m
[32m+[m[32m- Contains "pay" but not "UPI" → might miss it[m
[32m+[m[32m- What about "GPay", "PhonePe", "Paytm"? New terms every month[m
[32m+[m[32m- Can't handle: multilingual, typos, context[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mAI-based:[m
[32m+[m[32m- Understands "phone pay" = "UPI"[m
[32m+[m[32m- Handles variations naturally[m
[32m+[m[32m- Learns from data[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### B) Basic Keyword Matching Fails[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mComplaint: "I don't want to complain, but my card got blocked"[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mKeywords: "complain", "blocked", "card"[m
[32m+[m[32mExpected: Card issue - HIGH severity[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mBut the customer is being POLITE - they don't want to complain[m
[32m+[m[32mKeyword matcher would incorrectly flag this as "Angry"[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### C) Can't Handle Language Diversity[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mEnglish: "UPI payment failed"[m
[32m+[m[32mHindi:   "UPI पेमेंट फेल हो गया"[m
[32m+[m[32mMarathi: "UPI पेमेंट फेल झालं"[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mRule-based: Need separate rules for each language[m
[32m+[m[32mAI: Handles all three naturally[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### D) No Way to Detect Systemic Issues[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mBank's internal systems would show:[m
[32m+[m[32m- 47 separate UPI complaints from Nagpur[m
[32m+[m[32m- 23 separate UPI complaints from Mumbai[m
[32m+[m[32m- Each handled individually[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mBut ComplaintIQ's root cause detection finds:[m
[32m+[m[32m- 70 UPI complaints are actually ONE systemic issue[m
[32m+[m[32m- 50 are from Nagpur region → local gateway problem[m
[32m+[m[32m- This is actionable intelligence![m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## 3. The Solution Architecture - Layer by Layer[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Layer 1: Data Ingestion[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m[32mRaw Input Sources                    Normalized Format[m
[32m+[m[32m─────────────────                   ──────────────────[m
[32m+[m[32mEmail         ──────────────────►[m
[32m+[m[32mWhatsApp      ──────────────────►    {[m
[32m+[m[32mTwitter       ──────────────────►     complaint_text: str,[m
[32m+[m[32mPhone Call    ──────────────────►     channel: str,[m
[32m+[m[32mBranch        ──────────────────►     language: str,[m
[32m+[m[32mBank Portal   ──────────────────►     date: str,[m
[32m+[m[32mMobile App   ──────────────────►     location: str,[m
[32m+[m[32m                                     account_type: str,[m
