[32m+[m[32m                                    }[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**Why normalize?** Each channel has different formats:[m
[32m+[m[32m- Email: Subject, body, attachments[m
[32m+[m[32m- Twitter: 280 chars, mentions, hashtags[m
[32m+[m[32m- WhatsApp: Text, maybe voice note[m
[32m+[m[32m- Branch: Paper form, handwritten[m
