[32m+[m[32m## 16. The Database: SQLite Persistence[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### What is SQLite?[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mSQLite is a **lightweight file-based database**. Think of it as a spreadsheet stored in a file - simple, fast, and no server required.[m
